T02TD2738E:125b-1: a'a ry'a ba lo ke te shva ra sto tra /
T02TD2738E:125b-3: 'phags pa spyan ras gzigs dbang phyug la bstod pa /
T02TD2738E:125b-4: 'jig rten mgon po la phyag 'tshal lo //
T02TD2738E:125b-5: 'jig rten bla ma srid pa gsum gyis bstod pa po //
T02TD2738E:125b-6: lha yi gtso bo bdud dang tshangs pas bstod pa po //
T02TD2738E:125b-7: thub pa'i rgyal mchog bstod pas grub par mdzad pa po //
T02TD2738E:125b-8: 'jig rten gsum gyi mgon po mchog la phyag 'tshal lo //
T02TD2738E:125b-9: bde gshegs dpag med sku mchog sku bzang 'dzin pa po//
T02TD2738E:125b-10: bde gshegs snang mtha' yas kyi dbu rgyan 'dzin pa po //
T02TD2738E:125b-11: phyag g-yas mchog sbyin yi dags bkres skom sel ba po //
T02TD2738E:125b-12: g-yon pa'i phyag ni gser gyi padmos brgyan pa po //
T02TD2738E:125b-13: dri zhim ral ba'i phreng ba dmar ser 'khyug pa po //
T02TD2738E:125b-14: zhal ras rgyas pa zla ba lta bur mdzes pa po //
T02TD2738E:125b-15: spyan gyi padmo mchog tu bzang zhing yangs pa po //
T02TD2738E:125b-16: kha ba dung ltar rnam dkar dri ngad ldang ba po //
T02TD2738E:125b-17: dri med 'od chags mu tig tshom bu 'dzin pa po //
T02TD2738E:125b-18: mdzes pa'i 'od zer skya rengs dmar po sa brgyan pa po //
T02TD2738E:125b-19: padma'i mtsho ltar phyag ni dngar bar byas pa po //
T02TD2738E:125b-20: ston ka'i sprin gyi mdog dang ldan zhing gzhon pa po //
T02TD2738E:125b-21: rin chen mang pos dpung pa gnyis ni brgyan pa po //
T02TD2738E:125b-22: lo ma'i mchog ltar phyag mthil gzhon zhing 'jam pa po //
T02TD2738E:125b-23: ri dags pags pas nu ma g-yon pa bkab pa po //
T02TD2738E:125b-24: snyan cha gdu bus sgeg cing rgyan rnams 'chang ba po //
T02TD2738E:125b-25: dri ma med pa'i padmo'i mchog la gnas pa po //
T02TD2738E:125b-26: lte ba'i ngos ni padma'i 'dab ltar 'jam pa po //
T02TD2738E:125b-27: gser gyi rkang gdub sgra yis zhabs yid 'ong ba po //
T02TD2738E:125b-28: gser gyi ska rags mchog la nor bus spras pa po //
T02TD2738E:125b-29: sta zur dkris pa'i ras bzang sham thabs 'dzin pa po //
T02TD2738E:126a-0: thub pa'i mkhyen mchog mtsho chen pha rol phyin @126a * //
T02TD2738E:126a-2: mchog brnyes bsod nams mang po nye bar bsags pa po //
T02TD2738E:126a-3: rtag tu bde ba'i 'byung gnas rga nad sel ba po //
T02TD2738E:126a-4: gsum thar mdzad cing mkhas spyod spyod pa ston pa po //
T02TD2738E:126a-5: lus can mchog ste bdud dpung 'khrugs las rgyal pa po //
T02TD2738E:126a-6: tshangs pa'i gnas pa bzhi yis dben par mdzad pa po //
T02TD2738E:126a-7: ngang pa'i 'gros dang glang chen dregs 'drar gshegs pa po //
T02TD2738E:126a-8: tshogs kun nye bar bsags nas chos kun ston pa po //
T02TD2738E:126a-9: sdug bsngal mtsho dang nyon mongs mtsho las sgrol ba po //
T02TD2738E:126a-10: gang zhig rtag tu tho rangs langs nas gus pa yis //
T02TD2738E:126a-11: spyan ras gzigs kyi dbang po yid la sems byed cing //
T02TD2738E:126a-12: bstod pa'i mchog 'di dag cing gsal bar 'don byed na //
T02TD2738E:126a-13: de ni skyes pa'am yang na bud med yin yang rung //
T02TD2738E:126a-14: skye ba 'di dang ma 'ongs skye ba thams cad du //
T02TD2738E:126a-15: 'jig rten 'jig rten las 'das dgos pa kun 'grub 'gyur //
T02TD2738E:126a-16: 'phags pa spyan ras gzigs dbang phyug la bstod pa /
T02TD2738E:126a-17: dge slong ma dpal mos mdzad pa rdzogs so//
